		  <!-- Learning objectives and concepts to learn -->
		  <h2>Learning Objectives</h2>
		  <ol>
		    <li>Learn what is an inertial frame.</li>
		    <li>Learn Einstein's special relativity postulates.</li>
		    <li>Learn definition of an Event</li>
		  </ol>
		  
		  <!-- background knowledge -->
                  <h2>Lets recall some concepts </h2>
		  <em> Fill in the blancks</em> <br>
		  <b> Rules</b>: those than know what to fill in =<b> shout it out</b>. Those that does not =  <b> raise your hand</b>.
		  <br>
		  <br>
		  Lets practice first:<br>
		  Special Relativity was proposed and developed by ____________.
		  <br>
